name: {DD} Tiptoes standing doggy
description:
My first Lora) I wanted to make it better, but it's really hard to find a good source images.

I recomend using weights somewhere between 0.6-1.

Tags

There are should be some differences when you'll use this words (you doesn't have to use it):

tiptoesFuck, from side, from front, from behind, bent, standing, penis

Also I recomend using:

sex, standing_doggystyle

And for the negatives:

Loli, dwarf, hug, 2girls, 2boys, threesome, yuri

There are lots of arm grab and hair pulling in the source images. But for some reason i couldn't been able to invoke them.

Versions differencies

  • v1 is generic version

  • v2 New verion, which is slightly better with limbs, charactrers bodies and position. (I haven't used upscale on the examples for this version)

  • v3 Just works better, but affects style much stronger. I don't know why, but it works bad in anything v4.5. You can use weight 0.8-1 for anything, and then use imgToimg for details. Worked out for me.

  • v4 Now it gives you more control but also it's much harder to trigger. HiresFix sometimes better. Sometimes not)

*still trying to make it work as intended, so I hope I'll make a better version someday

Good results are unstable, you'll get a 2 good images out of 10 or less. So it needs some patience) Also ImgToImg randomly fixing some strange limb connections.

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)

Also my wet hair Lora was banned here, I dunno why. You can download the last version of it from my patreon for free.
